                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
                </listAnnotation>
                <listAnnotation xml:lang="en" type="notes">
                    
                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p><rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_407">Willemien</rs> was staying with <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_412">Anna</rs>.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>Vincent and Theo spent Christmas with their <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_524 bio.xml#_526">parents</rs> in Etten. Vincent arrived on Thursday, 23 or Friday, 24 December and left for Paris on Monday, 3 January 1876 (FR b2382 and b2225).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
